Noma iyiphi inkokhiso ekhokhwa ngumthengi kumphakeli ngokushintshisana ngesitifiketi se-prepaid , ikhadi , i-credit , ivawusha noma enye idivayisi efanayo okuchazwe esigatshaneni iyimpahla yomthwali waleso sitifiketi , ikhadi , i-credit , ivawusha noma idivayisi efanayo kuze kube sezingeni lapho umthengi engakayidonsi ngokushintshisana ngezimpahla noma amasevisi noma ukutholakala kwezimpahla esikhathini esizayo . 
