IBHUKWANA NGOKUSEBENZA KWEPHALAMENDE  
IPhalamende Labantu lidlulise imithetho elungile , kanye nokwengamela isigungu esiphezulu sikahulumeni , njengoba libabele ukwenza ngcono izinga lempilo yabantu base Ningizimu Afrika , nokwakha iNingizimu Afrika ebumbene nekhululekile . 
Siyethemba kuzokwenza ngcono kuphinde kuthuthukise ukuxhumana nathi , ukuze wena ubambe iqhaza uphinde ube yingxenye kwiPhalamende Labantu . 
Ihhovisi likaNobhala ePhalamende linomthwalo wokuqinisekisa ukusebenza ngendlela kwePhalamende futhi liqinisekisa ukuba khona kwezinto zokusebenza ezanele nokuqondisa ukuze kube khona imithetho nokwesekwa kwemisebenzi yePhalamende mayelana neziqondiso ezibekwe yilabo abanegunya lokwenza izinqumo . 
Ihhovisi likaNobhala  
Isifundazwe ngasinye kweziyisishiyagalolunye zaseNingizimu Afrika sithumela amaLungu ayisithupha azosebenza ngokugcwele kuMkhandlu kaZwelonke weziFundazwe . 
Idivishini YoMkhandlu Wezifundazwe Kazwelonke inikeza uxhaso ngenqubo nemisebenzi ephathelene neNdlu Yomkhandlu Kazwelonke Wezifundazwe naMalungu ibuye ibhekelele ukuhlanganyela kukahulumeni wasekhaya nowezifundazwe kwizingxoxo Zomkhandlu Kazwelonke Wezifundazwe . 
