IZINSIZAKALO EZINGATHOLWA UMPHAKATHI  
Uhambo olunomuntu okubonisayo ePhalamende lukunika incazelo ngokuthi iPhalamende lisebenza kanjani futhi uthola umlando ngemvelaphi yalesi sikhungo . 
Isikhalazo kofanele sifakwe iLungu bese sisayindwa ekuqaleni yiLungu lelo . 
Uma umuntu enze isicelo sokufinyelela ngandlela thize kwifomu , umfakisicelo uyovunyelwa ukufinyelela kulolo lwazi ngendlela abefake ngayo isicelo , inqobo nje uma ukwenza njalo kungeke kulimaze irekhodi ,noma kulimaze igunya lobunikazi elingekho ngaphansi kwePhalamende . 
Izikhalazo zisetshenziselwa ukudonsa amehlo ePhalamende ngezinto ezikhathaza umphakathi noma kucelwa iPhalamende ukuthi lithathe izinyathelo ezithile ngegunya elinalo . 
Lowo ofaka isicelo kumele asebenzise ifomu eliesemthethweni eyayibhalwe ePhephandabeni Likahulumeni elingunombolo 23805 lango mhla zingama 30 enyangeni ka Ncwaba ka 2002 . 
