UKhomishane akayona inhlangano entsha ngokuphelele , njengoba ezobandakanya ukwandiswa kwegunya leSikhundla Sokuvikelwa Kwabathengi , njengamanje elithuthukiswa ngaphakathi we-dti . 
UMthetho-Sivivinyo washicilelwa ku-Somqulu ukuze umphakathi uveze izimvo zawo futhi kwabe sekuthintwana nabathile ngaphakathi eminyangweni kahulumeni , abaqondisi beziyingi ezithie , izinhlangano zezezimboni , amaqembu abathengi , izinhlangano zezemfundo , izinyunyana kanye nabanye abantu abanesithakazelo . 
Njengoba sazi ukuthi ohulumeni bakazwelonke nabezifundazwe banamakhono esishayamthetho asetshenziswa ngokubambisana maqondana nokuvikelwa kwabathengi , kuye kwaqale kwathintwana nezifundazwe ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi kukhona ukuvumelana kabanzi ngalo Mthetho-Sivivinyo nokuthi ukukhathazeka okungase kube khona ngomthetho-sisekelo kuyabhekelwa . 
Ukwenza kube lula ukulethwa kwesixazululo nokudalwa koxolo ngenxa yezingxabano eziphakama ngokwemibandela yalo Mthetho ; 
akhe noma agunyaze imithetho ykusebenza ngokuphathelene nalo Mthetho futhi akhuthaze ukuqwasha komphakathi ngezindaba zokuvikelwa kwabathengi ; 
