ISITHWALAMBIZA NENYANGA  
Ngesikhathi izama ukuzikhulula , isithwalambiza sizosiphuthuma bese sicacela phezu kwenyanga , sigibele ngokunqoba sinqamula isibhakabhaka . 
Manje sengikutholile ! 
kodwa sawela phezu kwamagatsha futhi , lapho sahlala siphoxekile sibuka inyanga intweza inqamula isibhakabhaka yaze yanyamalala kwase kungena ukusa . Ezinsukwini ezilandelayo ngemva kwalo mzamo wokuqala , isithwalambiza sabuyela sayobhekisisa iminyakazo yenyanga . 
Ngizozama futhi , sasho , sase sivala amehlo okwesikhashana sizilungiselela ukugxuma kakhudlwana . 
Sacosha itshe salijikijela esizibeni ngokuthukuthela . 
Cha , hhayi lokho . 
Icebo lesithathu kwakuwukunqamula isikhonkwane , sisilole ngakwelinye icala sibe sesisifaka enhlabathini esicongweni sentaba . 
Ngizokuthola wena , nyanga , kwasho isithwalambiza , ngezimpiko ezibhebhezelayo , sashiya umngamanzi sandizela ezinyaweni zomkhomo . 
Ngalobo busuku sazifihla ezihlahleni lapho sabukela khona inyanga ihamba kancane iqonde esikhonkwaneni . 
Umphrofethi kwakungumuntu ongcwele owayekwazi ukubona okwakuzokwenzeka . 
Igama lesithwalambiza lesiLungu elithi mantis livela enkulumeni yasendulo yolimi lwesiGreki esho ukuthi umphrofethi . 
Kungenzekani , kucabanga sona , uma ngobunye ubusuku inyanga inganyamalala ingabe isa phuma futhi ? 
Kodwa kwakukhona into eyayizosimangaza : uma sifinyelela esicongweni somuthi , inyanga yayibukeka ikude kakhulu . 
Ngesikhathi inyanga iphakama ingenhla kwaso , iqondene ngqo nalapho sasicashe khona sajikijela idjani ngawo wonke amandla aso esibhakabhakeni . 
Safika esiqwini somngamanzi , sase siqala ngokushesha okukhulu ukucaca isiqu . 
Ngokunjalo , futhi zikhumbula nesincane esasinezimpiko ezimfushane esasifisa ukuba yisithixo . 
Kungesikhathi lapho amathunzi akusihlwa ayeseqala ukuphuma ngaphansi kwamatshe lapho ayecashe khona , ngesikhathi ilanga lishisa kakhulu emini . 
AbaThwa babethatha isithwalambiza njengesidalwa esikhethekile esinokwenza umlingo . 
nokuthi futhi , sasingasafuni ukugibela inyanga . 
Okwenzeka nje wukuthi isikhonkwane sama nje saba yisithunzi eside , esizacile enhlabathini lapho-ke inyanga yayizihambela inqamula isibhakabhaka , phezulu le . 
Leliya cebo alisebenzanga kahle njengoba bengicabange ukuthi lizosebenza , kwasho isithwalambiza , sibukeka sidangele nokho . 
Futhi kwakubakhona izikhathi lapho yayingabibikho nhlobo khona . 
Yingalesi sikhathi-ke lapho sazibona khona ukuthi sasiyisiphukuphuku kangakanani ; 
Saqala ukweluka intombo ngotshani obomile sase senza umgibe ngayo leyo ntambo sayibophela echosheni lenduku ende . 
Ngesikhathi inyanga iphuma ikhuphukela esibhakabhakeni izozihlabisa esikhonkwaneni bese ibambeka khona . 
Isithwalambiza sacathama ngokucophelela siya phambili saze sazithola sesibuka indilingiliza ecwebezelayo yenyanga intanta phansi esizibeni . 
Nazo-ke , wena siphukuphuku senyanga ! kwamamatheka isithwalambiza . 
Isithwalambiza saqaphela ukuthi inyanga yayiba nezigaba ezahlukene njengoba yayikhuphukela esibhakabhakeni , ngakho-ke sazitshela ukuthi into okwakufanele ukuthi siyenze wukuyibamba isasuka , uma isaqala ilunguza phezu komkhathizwe . 
Sema ngoba nenyanga yayilapho nayo , yayibanjwe emanzini . 
Ngisho nezinyoni zase busuku ezikwazi ukundizela phezulu imbala zazingakwazi ukufinyelela kuyo , pho-ke isilwanyana esincane kangaka nezimpikwana ezibhebhezelayo ezimfushane sasicabanga ukuthi sasizofinyelela kanjani lapho ? 
Idjani lenziwa ngomhlanga omude , uphaphe lwethendele kanye netshe konke kuboshelelwe ndawonye ngomsipha omfushane osontiwe . 
Kodwa ngesikhathi sifinyelela esicongweni sesihlahla inyanga yase yenyukile futhi . 
Saqala ngokubona amathunzi ezihlahla zomngamanzi esihlabathini , sase sibona izinyoni zitshwiza obala futhi ngejubane zinqamula esibhakabhakeni . 
Ngiyabonga , nyanga , kusho isithwalambiza ngokuzithoba , sisho sikhothamela isibhakabhaka . 
Sakwazi ukubuyela ogwini lapho safike sama siqhaqhazela , simanzi futhi sididekile . 
Kwakukhona isithwalambiza isifiso saso esikhulu okwakuwukuhlala enyangeni uma ilokhu ishwibeka esibhakbhakeni njalo ebusuku . 
Kungani sema , kungenzeka ubuze ? 
Amehlo ami abo ! khukhala isithwalambiza simemeza . 
Sathola ukuthi yayilokhu ishintshashintsha , isibonelo nje , iphuma emva kwesikhathi njalo ebusuku futhi njalo uma eyibona yayiba ncane bese iba nkulu futhi . 
Kufanele ngiyihlakaniphele le nyanga , sasilokhu sizitshela lokho , yingakho nje seza neCebo Lesine . 
Ngabe zonke izilwanyana zasebusuku ezisogwadule zingaphila kanjani ngaphandle kwenkazimulo yenyanga ezelekelela ngokuthi zithole ukudla ? 
Njalo isithwalambiza sasiphupha ngokuthi sizojabula kanjani uma sizibona sibuka phansi eKalahari Desert eyomile lapho sasihlala khona , inhliziyo yaso yayizojabula kanjani uma sibheka sinqamula imisele yamanzi engenalutho nemihlambi yezinsephe yeluka phakathi kwemingamanzi . 
Inyanga yaqala ukuphuma . 
Yingakho sabonakala sesime phambi komgodi wamanzi ogwadule ngemva kwehora . 
Ngokuhamba kwesikhathi uma ilokhu ikhuphukela esibhakabhakeni ihamba ngokushesha futhi kaningi ngaphambi kwentathakusa , izonyamalala ingene emafini nangaphambi kokufinyelela emkhathizweni . 
Noma kunjalo , saziphonsa phezulu emoyeni sichaye izandla ; 
Izehlakalo ozofunda ngazo zenzeka emandulo lapho imihlambi emikhulu yezindlovu nezinyamazane zazizulazula , zinqamula amathafa omile aseHeikum okuyigama lelo abantu abangabaThwa abaliqamba iKalahari Desert . 
Engikudingayo-ke manje yindlela entsha yokwenza izinto , nokuyilapho-ke seza necebo lokuzama ukucupha inyanga . 
Kungoba sasomiwe sidinga okuphuzwayo ? 
Impela , kwacabanga isithwalambiza , uma ngiphonsa idjani emoyeni lizozithandela ngenyanga bese kuthi isisindo setshe siwisele le nyanga lapha phansi eMhlabeni ? 
Laphuma esandleni saso nje ngesiswebhu . 
Ngaphandle nje kokuthi izinto azizange zibe njengoba isithwalambiza sasilindele , ngoba , sathi uma sijikijela intambo yaso enefindo emoyeni , ivele iziwele ingenalutho . 
Sasifuna nje ukuthi siphinde sibone emehlweni nokuthi ubuhlungu esasibuzwa buphele . 
Ngakusasa ekuseni ubuhlungu baphela nokubona kwesithwalambiza kwabuya . 
Uma idjani liphoswa emoyeni libuya lijikeleza phansi enhlabathi njengekhasi lomkhiwane . 
Laya phezulu kakhulu impela , laselibuya liwela phezu kwamagatsha futhi , uphaphe lwaphephezelela emakhasini njengenyoni encane elimele . 
Isithwalambiza saqeda bonke lobo busuku simile sithandaza , sintengantenga kancane , sincenga inyanga ukuthi isiphe ukubona kwaso futhi . 
Yingakho zonke izithwalambiza zanamuhla zihlala imilenze yazo yangaphambili yemboze ubuso : zidumisa inyanga eyaxolela ukhokho wazo futhi yabuyisela nokubona kwakhe . 
Ngeke ngiyeke manje , kwasho isithwalambiza saqala sagibela . 
Mina , ngihlakaniphe kakhulu . 
Yase igaxeke emagatsheni omkhomo owawuseduze . 
Kodwa kuthe uma sibheka futhi sabona inyanga ibukeka ikude kakhulu kunakuqala . 
Sabhadazela sihlehlela emva singasaboni emehlweni , sisuka emseleni wamanzi sayowela ezihlahleni lapho safike sazama ukuhlikihla amehlo ukususa izingcezwana emehlweni , kodwa akukho okwakuzodambisa ubuhlungu . 
Kakade , nalokho akuzange kusebenze , okwadala ukuthi sithukuthele kakhulu futhi . 
Kuzothi uma inyanga isingenhla kwaso sizosuka lapho sicashe khona sigijima , sijikijele inyanga ngomgibe wentambo bese sikotela kuyona sikhuphukele phezulu . 
Ngabe iyiphi indlela eyayingaba lula ukwedlula lena ? 
Buya la , kwamemeza isithwalambiza , sinyakazisa inqindi emoyeni , kodwa amazwi aso avele ankenteza nje ebumnyameni . 
Leli cebo lalifake ukusetshenziswa kwe djani , okuyithoyizi lezingane zabaThwa . 
Isithwalambiza uma sibona ukuthi inyanga ibambeke emagatsheni omngamanzi oseduze , saphuma lapho sasicashe khona saqonda enhlabathini . 
Leso yisikhathi lapho inyanga yayisebucayini khona ngesikhathi inkulu , isinda futhi ihamba kancane . 
Ngaso sonke isikhathi , isithwalambiza sazifihla emagatsheni emithi emide sibuka inyanga intweza inqamula esibhakabhakeni , sasilokhu sizame njalo ukuthi siyibambe kodwa asizange siphumelele . 
Ngakusasa isthwalambiza saqala senza esabe sikuhlelile kwicebo laso . 
Kodwa isithwalambiza kwakuyisinambuzane nje futhi inyanga yayikude kakhulu . 
Sasifuna ukwenza lokhu yikhona sasizobukela phansi zonke ezinye izilwane ogwadule . 
Leli cebo lami ngeke lehluleke , kwasho isithwalambiza , sibukeka siziqhenya kakhulu . 
