Sasingazi thina ukuthi lo mcimbi , wangomhla ka 3 kuJanuwari 2009 kwakungowokugcina ukuhlangana nenkosi uMbongeleni Zondi isaphila . 
> > Inkosi uMbongeleni Zondi yakhothama ngesikhathi lapho izinhlelo zikaHulumeni , zokuthuthukisa ubuholi bomdabu esiFundazweni ziqala ukuthela izithelo . 
Ngonyaka ka 1994 kwasungulwa iNingizimu Afrika yentando yeningi . 
Inkosi uMbongeleni Zondi wayewuphawo oluhle oluphemba ubudlelwano , okuwuphawu oluhle olukhomba ukuthi inkosi kufanele kube umuntu onjani kulezi zinsuku ekuthuthukiseni izimpilo zabantu bayo . 
Ngaphezu kwalokho , izikhulu ezivela ku-Greater Manchester Police seziqeqeshe amavolontiya azokwenza umsebenzi wokuhamba ehlola ubugebengu . 
Okuningi kwalokhu inkosi uBhambatha yikho eyayikuphilela , futhi yakulwela yaze yakufela , esesikuzuzile manje . 
Ukuphakwa kwala mavolontiya athunyelwa ezindaweni ezithile ezikhethekile . 
Inkosi uMbongeleni Zondi naye usocongwe ngesihluku elokishini laseMlazi , ezinsukwini nje eziyisishiyagalolunye ezidlule , ngomhla ka 22 kuMasingana . 
Ngomhla ka 11 kuNhlangulana 2006 , sasihlangene khona lapha eNgome sizozwakalisa ukuhlehliswa nokuguqulwa kwesinqumo sika Lusibalukhulu wamakoloni aseNatali , esaphasiswa ngomhla ka 23 kuNhlolanja ngo 1906 , esasiphuca Inkosi uBhambatha Zondi ubukhosi  besizwe sakwaZondi . 
Izifunda ezisasele nazo zizolithola lolu hlelo . 
Ngakho Inkosi uZondi yabuyiselwa esikhundleni sayo sobukhosi , seyakhothama , yilo Hulumeni wethu onakekelayo . 
Lokhu kuhambisana noMthetho woBuholi beNdabuko noHlelo LokuBusa walapha KwaZulu-Natali , uMthetho ka 2003 kanye noMthetho walapha KwaZulu-Natali wobuHoli beNdabuko kanye nokuBusa ka 2005 . Ngokokuqala ngqa , abesifazane nentsha sebelindeleke ngokusemthethweni ukuthi bangabamba iqhaza ezindabeni eziphathelene nezikhungo zendabuko . 
Nokho , sinethemba neqholo lokuthi , uma sibambene , singayiguqula yonke le nto , silwe nobugebengu , futhi siyaphumelela kulowo mkhankaso wethu . 
Kanti futhi zonke izindleko zokuhamba  zamaKhosi zakhushulwa ukuze zilingane nalezo ezihlelwe umNyango wezokuThutha . 
Lokhu kwenziwa ngokubambisana nophiko lwamaPhoyisa ethu iSouth African Police Service . 
Siphila esikhathini sethemba lokuthula , sentando yeningi kanye nesentuthuko . 
Wayengumuntu owayekuqhakambisa ubuqhawe namasiko nokuguqula amanye amasiko ukuba avumelane nesikhathi samanje . 
Ngonyaka ka 2008 , umNyango kaHulumeni waseKhaya kanye neziNdaba zeNdabuko waqasha abaQondisi bazo zonke iziNdlu zobuHoli beNdabuko nezaseKhaya . 
Ngempela , silahlekelwe umholi obeletha intuthuko futhi elwela inguquko , Inkosi eyayibeka izidingo zabantu bayo kuqala , owayebona uhulumeni engumlingani wentuthuko yabantu nendawo yayo . 
La mavolontiya asebenza ngokubambisana namaphoyisa ukuqinisekisa ukuthi abantu baphephile emiphakathini yabo . 
Ubugebengu , nezenzo zobugebengu , inkinga enkulu le ekhathaza imiphakathi yethu . 
Kulowo mhlangano kwaphenjwa ama-Joint Coordination Committees phakathi komasipala nemikhandlu yabaholi bendabuko . 
Wayelwela intuthuko nenkululeko ebuphofini babantu bakhe , okuyinto ayincela kuyisemkhulu , Inkosi uBhambatha Zondi . 
Ukuphumelela komgubho ka 2006 wokukhumbula Inkosi uBhambatha kwaba ubuhlakani nomsebenzi wenkosi uMbongeleni Zondi ngokuba neso elibuka impilo ngeso elinobuhlakani . 
Emuva kokubonisana kabanzi , iVolunteer Social Crime Prevention Programme yaqala ukuhlolwa komasipala abathile ababekhethiwe abafana nomasipala wasoGu , Uthukela , Amajuba , Ethekwini , Umgungundlovu kanye noMkhanyakude . 
