Ngakwezomnotho , ukutshalwa kwezimali emisebenzini yezwe kanye nakumabhizinisi azimeleyo kukhule ngamapesenti ayishuminanye kanti-ke imali esetshenzisiwe ekwakheni izinto ezisetshenziswa ngumphakathi yona ikhule ngo 15 .8 . 
Kodwa-ke sasiphindesazi ukuthi wayenomoya wempikelelo nesifiso esikhulu sokuqhubeka aphile phakathi kwethu . Besinenhloso yokumamukela kanye namalungu omndeni wakhe njengezivakashi zethu kulomcimbi kwenyanga kaNcwaba , kodwa-ke akuzange kubenjalo .  
Ukufaka isandla ekucazululweni kwezinkinga ezibhekene nabantu bonke emhlabeni . 
Ukufa kwakhe kwakuyomfihlakalo kanti futhi kwahlasimulisa umzimba , kodwa-ke impilo yakhe kwakuyisibonelo esihle esasiholela kulenkululeko esiyithokozelayo namhlanje . 
